[normal]2.7.
[normal]&#xa0; 
[normal]Any operations funded by the public should satisfy the criteria of efficiency, effectiveness and economy.  
[normal]2.8.
[normal]&#xa0; 
[normal]The scope, scale and remit of a publicly funded broadcaster should 
[normal]be 
[normal]the minimum necessary to meet its purpose.  
[normal]2.9.
[normal]&#xa0; 
[normal]Output and services should be determined on the basis of demand and demand should be measured by the willingness of viewers to pay for the service.  
[normal]2.10.
