[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]The BBC’s defamation of 
[normal]Lord McAlpine.
[normal]Summary[bold]The broadcasting market has changed signifi
[normal]cantly since the BBC was first established
[normal].
[normal] 
[normal] With the wide range of providers now in the broadcast market a new model is required for the provision of ‘public service’ broadcasting and funding of the BBC.  The current system of a compulsory tax on all UK households to fund the BBC is both regressive
[normal] and detrimental to the good management of the organization.  The BBC tax should be abolished and the BBC funded through subscription and / or advertising.  Such a system will resolve many of the governance failures evident in the current arrangements.
[normal]&#xa0;[bold]December 2013
